  "title": "Microbiologist (Office hours, up to $4K) #HTJ",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Develop and maintain environmental monitoring program and microbiological laboratory procedures.</p></li><li><p>Carry out environmental and material microbiological tests as required.</p></li><li><p>Test water samples</p></li><li><p>Lead test method verification of microbiological method.</p></li><li><p>Maintain up-to-date, complete and precise worksheets of all tests performed.</p></li><li><p>Participate and support audit preparation and audit responses</p></li><li><p>Participate in all compliance-related matters,</p></li><li><p>Any other tasks as and when assigned</p></li><li></li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li><p>Diploma in Microbiologist or related courses</p></li><li><p>Minimum internship experience<br /><br /></p></li></ul><p><em>Interested candidates, please forward your resume to</em><em><strong> jalenetan@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></em><br /></p><p><em>Jalene Tan</em><br /><em>Outsourced Team</em><br /><em>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</em></p>",
